# Book Analytics API

A REST API built with FastAPI for managing and analyzing personal reading data stored in a CSV dataset.

The project combines backend API development with data analysis workflows using Pandas.

---

## Features

- Retrieve books by author
- Filter books dynamically using query parameters
- Pagination support
- Author-level analytics
- Global reading analytics
- Data validation using Pydantic schemas
- CSV-based data source

---

